- Prefer functional components with React hooks
- Leverage Expo SDK features and APIs effectively
- Use React Navigation for structured and navigation
- Manage assets efficiently with Expo's asset system (images, fonts, etc.)
- Error handling and implement crash reporting with Sentry
- Use Reanimated for performant animations